high_descs: Turn around to reach the kitchen and turn right to reach the end of the countertop to the right of the microwave.
Pick up the potato from the counter.
Head to the fridge on the left.
Cool the potato in the fridge and take it out.
Turn right to head to the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left. Approach the countertop. Turn left. Approach the countertop. Turn to the right. Reach the countertop and turn left.
Turn left. Continue ahead. Turn left. Move to the side of the fridge. Turn right.
Open the shelf. Place the potato on the first level on the left. Close the shelf for ten seconds. Open the doors. Grab the potato from the shelf. Close the doors.
Turn right. Go to the microwave. Turn left.
Open the microwave. Place the potato on the left side. Close the microwave with the potato inside.
anns.task_desc: Search for a potato. Place it first on a shelf and later in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the countertop across from the sink.
Pick up the potato from the countertop.
Turn to the left and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and put the potato on the lower shelf. Close the door and open the door. Take the potato out.
Turn to the right and walk to the microwave.
Open the door and put the potato in the microwave. Turn it on.
anns.task_desc: Move the potato from the countertop to the microwave.
